      "id": "mturk_agent_1",
      "turn_index": 2,
      "turn_id": "dialogue_00127_turn_02",
      "speaker": "mturk_agent_1",
      "listener": "mturk_agent_2"
    },
    {
      "text": "Well maybe we can work something out between us.  Our food and water was in the bags they loss so I really need those.  Do you think you could make do with 1 food and some water?",
      "task_data": {
        "data": "",
        "issue2youget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        },
        "issue2theyget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        }
      },
      "id": "mturk_agent_2",
      "turn_index": 3,
      "turn_id": "dialogue_00127_turn_03",
      "speaker": "mturk_agent_2",
      "listener": "mturk_agent_1"
    },
    {
      "text": "I really need 2 foods. I can do with 1 water or if you are in a giving mood then maybe I can have 2 waters? 🙂",
      "task_data": {
        "data": "",
        "issue2youget": {
          "Firewood": "",
          "Water": "",
          "Food": ""
        },
        "issue2theyget": {
          "Firewood": "",
